• Used to access each successive value of a data structure
• There must be a data structure (Array, or Collection or Map) to use for each loop
• Iteration times and orders are fixed
• Does not have index numbers
• for each loop: already iterated,  iteration starts from index 0

for(DataType variableName : dataStructure ){
//Statement
 }
**Data type must match with the successive values of the data structure
